




<h3>George W. Bush<i> (111552428)</i></h3><h1><i> 2006-01-31 - Speeches</i></h1>  A <a href='t2.html'><span title='2'>hopeful</span></a> <a href='t2.html'><span title='2'>society</span></a> <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>acts</span></a> boldly to <a href='t7.html'><span title='7'>fight</span></a> <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>diseases</span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'>like</span></a> HIV/AIDS, <a href='t10.html'><span title='10'>which</span></a> can be <a href='t14.html'><span title='14'>prevented</span></a> and <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>treated</span></a> and <a href='t7.html'><span title='7'>defeated</span></a>. More <a href='t12.html'><span title='12'>than</span></a> a <a href='t16.html'><span title='16'>million</span></a> <a href='t16.html'><span title='16'>Americans</span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'>live</span></a> with HIV, and <a href='t12.html'><span title='12'>half</span></a> of <a href='t15.html'><span title='15'>all</span></a> <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>AIDS</span></a> <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>cases</span></a> occur <a href='t5.html'><span title='5'>among</span></a> <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>African</span></a> <a href='t16.html'><span title='16'>Americans</span></a>. I <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>ask</span></a> <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>Congress</span></a> to <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>reform</span></a> and <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>reauthorize</span></a> the Ryan <a href='t4.html'><span title='4'>White</span></a> <a href='t18.html'><span title='18'>Act</span></a> and <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>provide</span></a> <a href='t13.html'><span title='13'>new</span></a> <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>funding</span></a> to <a href='t14.html'><span title='14'>States</span></a>, <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'>so</span></a> we <a href='t5.html'><span title='5'>end</span></a> the <a href='t2.html'><span title='2'>waiting</span></a> lists for <a href='t8.html'><